{
  "stem": "9730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hitler had told him that he was to take the bodies to the courtyard of the bunker and pour cans of gas over them and set them aflame, and make sure that-- that there would be no remains or as few remains as possible, so that they could not be desecrated.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or the Russians-- they expected the Russians to take this soon, that they would make something of that and use it for whatever the Russians would have used it for.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and he-- he claims to have carried out those instructions to the letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, his name was Erich Kempka-- K-E-M-P, I think, K-A.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because by that time, this was an accomplished fact, and he had really nothing to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I was to read many years thereafter, this is exactly the story he gave to other historians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he described it, but I suppose I didn't even ask him too much about the bunker because I-- it wasn't any-- anything I could have done with that information.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at any rate, I-- I-- I didn't have time to go into such details.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we were in-- in Metz, at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And surrounding the hills around Metz were mountains on which there were some forts in which the Germans held out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to-- we had to secure those forts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried for-- it took quite a number of weeks till we could neutralize them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then finally, the forts were ready to surrender.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I remember going in there to take the surrender of the forts.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
